            "hInfo": {
                "name": "New Shahana - Hostel",
                "des": "{\"amenities\":\"Make use of convenient amenities, which include complimentary wireless internet access and tour/ticket assistance.\",\"rooms\":\"Make yourself at home in one of the 20 air-conditioned guestrooms. Complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected, and cable programming is available for your entertainment. Bathrooms have showers and complimentary toiletries. Conveniences include phones, as well as safes and desks.\",\"onsite_payments\":\"Visa, Mastercard\",\"dining\":\"Take advantage of the hostel's 24-hour room service.\",\"business_amenities\":\"Featured amenities include express check-in, complimentary newspapers in the lobby, and a 24-hour front desk.\",\"location\":\"With a stay at New Shahana - Hostel in Mumbai (Andheri East), you'll be within a 10-minute drive of NESCO Center and U.S. Consulate General.  This hostel is 5.2 mi (8.4 km) from Jio World Convention Centre and 5.4 mi (8.6 km) from Juhu Beach.\",\"attractions\":\"Distances are displayed to the nearest 0.1 mile and kilometer.  MIDC Industrial Estate - 1 km / 0.6 mi  Powai Lake - 2.9 km / 1.8 mi  Mahakali Caves - 3 km / 1.9 mi  Hakone - 4.1 km / 2.5 mi  Sanjay Gandhi National Park - 4.1 km / 2.6 mi  Hiranandani Business Park - Powai - 4.6 km / 2.8 mi  Phoenix Market City Mall - 4.9 km / 3 mi  NESCO Center - 6.1 km / 3.8 mi  KidZania Mumbai - 6.4 km / 4 mi  Bombay Convention & Exhibition Centre - 6.4 km / 4 mi  R City Mall - 6.5 km / 4 mi  Andheri Sports Complex - 6.9 km / 4.3 mi  Nanavati Super Speciality Hospital - 7.3 km / 4.6 mi  NMIMS Mumbai - 7.4 km / 4.6 mi  Kokilaben Dhirubhai Ambani Hospital & Medical Research Institute - 7.6 km / 4.7 mi  The nearest major airport is Chhatrapati Shivaji International Airport (BOM) - 3.6 km / 2.2 mi\",\"headline\":\"In Mumbai (Andheri East)\"}",
